snippet.title: Fitting Exponential Functions to Data (TANTON Mathematics)
snippet.description: A standard unit in an algebra II or pre-calculus course is to find a exponential function that fits two data points. There is a hard way to do this, and there is an easy way - just write down the answer! I show you how.
